{
  "stem": "19939.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I saw that they-- they were walking without their shoes, only they were sitting on the something, coming around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was this mood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody ever explained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just found out by myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she, I think, was-- she had a miscarriage before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she probably was sick, or maybe she wasn't well when she was bringing me up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe she was depressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I think back, the life that I have now and the lives of people lead here, how hard it was, the whole atmosphere in Poland, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never went back at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember of an oppressive feeling, even as a child, maybe because I was sent away to the grandparents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember this vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the grandfather, I see him, how he came through the door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a big house, you know, first floor, and he appeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was something, screaming, and-- and going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember her mother hitting her--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were always-- so I was with my mother's parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My brother was with my father's parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were neighboring, you know, the town where my father lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then when I eventually came back and went to school and stayed till I run away, was in the middle, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, lets say you are Teaneck and to the left is Hackensack, to the right is Englewood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There might be 10, 12 kilometers distances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a-- a bus that was going from one city to another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's say starting with the bigger city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what is the-- the word?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was not cruising.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is for the bus?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the morning and in the evening there was a bus going.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
